# Ontology Parse API - HTTP 测试文件

### 根路径
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/
Accept: application/json

### 健康检查
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health
Accept: application/json

### 获取所有本体术语
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/ontology/terms
Accept: application/json

### 根据ID获取特定术语
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/ontology/terms/MS:0000001
Accept: application/json

### 搜索本体术语
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/ontology/terms/search?q=mass
Accept: application/json

### 获取本体统计信息
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/ontology/stats
Accept: application/json

### 导出本体数据为JSON文件
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/ontology/export
Accept: application/json

### API 文档
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs
Accept: text/html

### ReDoc 文档
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/redoc
Accept: text/html

### OpenAPI Schema
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/openapi.json
Accept: application/json
